Neviem.

39
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:28,810
Je stále pred mojim brlohom?

40
00:06:28,810 --> 00:06:30,210
Áno, teta.

41
00:06:30,210 --> 00:06:33,160
Stále vonku čelí slnko a dážď.

42
00:06:53,770 --> 00:06:55,290
Dijun...

43
00:06:56,310 --> 00:07:01,240
